               line containing the first item in the current
               selection list.

{B}End{N}            usually, to move the selected line to point to the
               line containing the last item in the current
               selection list.

{B}PgUp{N}           usually, to move the selected line to point to the
               line containing the previous item in the current
               selection list.

{B}PgDn{N}           usually, to move the selected line to point to the
               line containing the next item in the current
               selection list.

