               uses to create this display.

{B}F4{N}             to change the options TACT uses to create this
               display.

{B}Ctrl-F4{N}        to close the current display

{B}F7{N}             to change the top display to another currently
               open display.

{B}F9{N}             to synchronize all the open displays so that they
